The paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence (AI) techniques for context understanding, which is a common topic in the field of AI. The paper specifically focuses on the use of hybrid AI methodology, which combines data-driven and knowledge-driven methods, and the concept of neuro-symbolism. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.AI. The paper also discusses the use of deep neural networks, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG. Additionally, the paper discusses natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) applications, which fall under the sub-categories of cs.CL and cs.CV, respectively. Finally, the paper discusses the use of neuro-symbolism in control systems, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SY.
